  <toolclip key="xgmCreateInteractiveGroomSplineBtn" title="创建头发和毛发" help="TC-Grooming-Create-Interactive-Groom-Splines">
    <text>使用交互式修饰样条线创建头发和毛发。</text>
	<expanded>
      <resourcelist>
        <link location="TC-Grooming-Interactive-Grooming-Overview">XGen 交互式修饰</link>
		<link location="TC-Grooming-Get-Started">XGen 交互式修饰入门</link>
